I"’<h2 id="github-repository-mining">GitHub Repository Mining</h2>

<p>In order to access the presence of security weaknesses in SaltStack scripts, the students need to mine repository from GitHub as most IT organizations hosts their Open Source Software (OSS) projects in GitHub. The GitHub repositories need to be curated with filteration criteria. The following figure shows the GitHub repository curation process. GitHub API allows user to mine repositories based on criterias.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/GH.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>In the following example, the highlighted red box denotes a security weakness in SaltStack scripts, presence hard-coded secrets/keys.</p>

